  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Kde-baseapps</title>

    <para>This package provides various applications, such as Dolphin 
    (file manager) and Konqueror (web browser). Infrastructure files and 
    libraries are also provided.</para>

    &lfs71_checked;

